# Frontend language detection
# Mark vendor and generated files as vendored to exclude from language stats
frontend/node_modules/** linguist-vendored
backend/htmlcov/** linguist-generated
**/playwright-report/** linguist-generated
**/test-results/** linguist-generated

# Mark test files as test code
**/*test*.html linguist-documentation
**/*test*.js linguist-documentation
**/tests/** linguist-documentation
**/*.spec.js linguist-documentation
**/*.test.js linguist-documentation

# Documentation files
*.md linguist-documentation
docs/** linguist-documentation

# Mark Dockerfile as configuration (not main language)
**/Dockerfile linguist-documentation
**/.dockerignore linguist-documentation
**/docker-compose.yml linguist-documentation
**/nginx*.conf linguist-documentation

# Ensure HTML and JavaScript are detected
*.html linguist-detectable
*.js linguist-detectable
*.css linguist-detectable
